/sys/devices/system/cpu/vulnerabilities/spectre_v2:Mitigation: Full generic retpoline, STIBP: disabled, RSB filling
</pre>
<p> </p>
<h2>Debian Buster</h2>
<p><img src="http://helio.loureiro.eng.br/images/stories/2020/Screenshot-debian.png" width="800" height="450"></p>
<p>uname:</p>
<pre>Linux debian 4.19.0-9-amd64 #1 SMP Debian 4.19.118-2 (2020-04-29) x86_64 GNU/Linux</pre>
<p> </p>
<p>cpuinfo:</p>
<pre>processor       : 0
